data.title: Mike Sullivan '91, T'97
data.text: Mike joined the DCIO in 2011 and co-manages the private equity and venture capital portfolios. Prior to Dartmouth, he was a partner at FLAG Capital Management, a private equity and venture capital fund of funds, and also worked at Cambridge Associates. Mike graduated from Dartmouth College in 1991 with an AB degree in economics and earned an MBA in 1997 from the Tuck School of Business at Dartmouth College.
